data.description: 5 Bedroom, 3 1/2 Bath Home, sitting on almost a Quarter Acre! Located in New Braunfels, TX! This home has all of the space your Family will ever need! Open Floor plan with Master Bedroom Downstairs! Office/Flex space, and 2 full baths upstairs. Lot sits on a greenbelt, with gated entry to possible store a boat. Close to Lake McQueeney, and easy access to I-35 for commuters! NBISD. Priced $28K below County appraised value, for INSTANT EQUITY!!
